submission.source:
I am currently a student from Vietnam. 
When I first found Cash-Cow was the first DAO project on Solana, I tried only $200 from my saving used for covid19 pandemic precaution. After more than a week, I could see the money flow moved to this project as DAO became popular with PEOPLE and SOS project. I borrowed more money from my friends and my family to invest in Cashio since then. However, I lost a lot and do not know what to do before this announcement for refund.
I would express my sincere thank to your refund from the bottom of my heart. Since I am still indebted about my borrowing, I hope for your charity would give me a helping hand too.
